# Ignore everything in 3D-Models/ (large binaries, working blends,
# sibling project models) EXCEPT for the third-party CC-BY provenance
# metadata under 3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/.
#
# Git requires walking the path: each parent dir must be un-ignored
# before its children can be re-included.
3D-Models/*
!3D-Models/HelmKit/
3D-Models/HelmKit/*
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/
3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/*
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/ATTRIBUTIONS.md
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/ATTRIBUTIONS.md
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/LICENSE.txt
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/README.txt
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/*.md
!3D-Models/HelmKit/_derived/**/*.svg
# Binary geometry (STL, .skp, .blend, etc.) inside _derived/ remains
# off-repo — operators re-fetch from Thingiverse if needed; LICENSE.txt
# + ATTRIBUTIONS.md preserve provenance.

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Local caches (link checker, wiki probe, etc.)
.cache/
